      <section eId="sec_20_3_240">
        <num>20-3-240</num>
        <content>
          <p>The commission shall submit its regular and supplemental budget requests to the Governor at such times and in such form and manner as required by state law; provided, however, that the commission shall, in accordance with Code Section 50-4-3, include in its budget requests the respective budget requests, if any, of the corporation and of the authority as prepared and submitted to the commission by the corporation and by the authority.</p>
